    "page.faq.subsection.benefits.joining.restoin": "What are the benefits of joining Resto-in?",
    "page.faq.subsection.benefits.joining.restoin.answer1": "Increase your turnover",
    "page.faq.subsection.benefits.joining.restoin.answer2": "Increase your notoriety with our marketing campaign",
    "page.faq.subsection.benefits.joining.restoin.answer3": "Get new clients",
    "page.faq.subsection.benefits.joining.restoin.answer4": "Secure the loyalty of your customers",
    "page.faq.subsection.combine.orders": "Can I combine orders from different restaurants?",
    "page.faq.subsection.combine.orders.answer": "No. You can’t make orders with more than one restaurant at a time. If you want to order different food from another restaurant, you need to complete a separate order.",
    "page.faq.subsection.create.account": "How can I create an account?",
    "page.faq.subsection.create.account.answer": "Click on the button “Create an account”.  Once you have registered with all your data you will be able to order in all restaurants you want.",
    "page.faq.subsection.delayed.delivery": "Delayed delivery",
    "page.faq.subsection.delayed.delivery.answer1": "Our restaurants do everything they can to get your food to you within 45 minutes.  On busy days, like the weekends, it can take a bit longer. ",
    "page.faq.subsection.delayed.delivery.answer2": "Check the delivery time on the confirmation email - if it’s been longer than 45 minutes, you can call our customer service. ",
    "page.faq.subsection.food.allergy": "What if i have a food allergy or special dietary requirement?",
    "page.faq.subsection.food.allergy.answer1": "Resto-in depends on our partnered restaurants to tell you about the particular ingredients from their dishes.",
    "page.faq.subsection.food.allergy.answer2": "We try to ensure that what they say is accurately copied on to our web site.",
    "page.faq.subsection.food.allergy.answer3": "However it is initially up to the restaurant themselves to provide accurate and correct information.",
    "page.faq.subsection.food.allergy.answer4": "If you have any doubts or just want to check, don’t hesitate to call our customer service.",
    "page.faq.subsection.food.allergy.answer5": "If you have any allergies or dietary requirements you can let the restaurant know in the comments box in your order or call our customer service. We will inform the restaurant. ",
    "page.faq.subsection.have.promotion.code": "I have a promotion code. How can i use it?",
    "page.faq.subsection.have.promotion.code.answer": "Select a restaurant",
    "page.faq.subsection.havent.received.refund": "I haven’t received my refund",
    "page.faq.subsection.havent.received.refund.answer": "Contact our customer service, one of our Resto-in agent will give you a quick answer.",
    "page.faq.subsection.how.can.contact": "How can i contact you?",
    "page.faq.subsection.how.can.contact.answer": "Phone - xxxxxxxxxxx - Monday to Sunday, 9am - 12am",
    "page.faq.subsection.how.long.prepare.food": "How long do I have to prepare the food?",
    "page.faq.subsection.how.long.prepare.food.answer": "The largest time period you have to make a food preparation is 25 - 30 minutes (it depend the distance between the restaurant and the client).  If you should ever experience any problems meeting this deadline, we would encourage you to call our customer service to let us know.",
    "page.faq.subsection.join.us": "Join us",
    "page.faq.subsection.join.us.answer": "Joining us is simple, just let us know you’re interested.",
    "page.faq.subsection.meal.unacceptable": "My meal was unacceptable. How can I claim a refund or compensation?",
    "page.faq.subsection.meal.unacceptable.answer": "If you did’nt enjoy your meal, please call us to understand what was the problem. It was the first time? The meal didn’t correspond with the description?",
    "page.faq.subsection.money.take.account": "When is money taken from my account?",
    "page.faq.subsection.not.received.confirmation.email": "I haven’t received my confirmation email",
    "page.faq.subsection.not.received.confirmation.email.answer1": "Don’t worry - there may just be a technical glitch, your order has probably gone through and there’s just a delay in your confirmation email.",
    "page.faq.subsection.not.received.confirmation.email.answer2": "If you want to check,or view your recent orders.",
